Special Events & Meetings
A Great Clubhouse and Scenic Course Views Provide the Perfect Backdrop for Your Event
From casual celebrations to corporate meetings, community events and receptions, Baytree National is the perfect venue to host your next event.
We offer beautiful surroundings and a casual event space with an inviting outdoor patio which can accommodate events. Our friendly and professional staff will assist with all the arrangements for your group.
Baytree offers affordable packages and personalized breakfast, lunch and dinner menus for any size budget. Menus range from delicatessen style buffets to hearty barbecues and more.
For information on hosting your next event at Baytree, please call
(321) 259-9060
or email
Inquiry@BaytreeNational.com
.

Golf Memberships
Flexible Memberships to Fit Your Lifestyle
Baytree National Golf Links offers a variety of affordable memberships to fit your lifestyle. Members enjoy championship golf on our award-winning Gary Player Signature Course with new CHAMPION Dwarf Bermudagrass greens, found on 12 PGA Tour venues including Pinehurst No. 2.
Our management and staff are dedicated to providing you with the highest level of service and the best golfing membership on the Space Coast. Member benefits include:
Award-Winning Gary Player Signature Course
Tour-Quality Practice Facilities
PGA Instruction
14-Day Advance Tee Times
Annual Private Cart Plan Available
Men’s and Women’s Golf Associations
Member Leagues, Tournaments & Events
Stylish Clubhouse with Great Food and a Full Bar
Reciprocal Playing Privileges at other Florida Golf Trail® Clubs
Toss in camaraderie and great rounds of golf and you’ve got the makings of a wonderful golf membership!
For more information on Membership opportunities at Baytree National Golf Links, please call
(321) 259-9060
or email
Inquiry@BaytreeNational.com
.
